Warning:
The European drug checking group that analyzed this sample issued a warning because it contains a drug other than the one it was represented as.

In raveitsafe and SaferParty's alert for this sample, they note: 'This substance, sold as a synthetic hashish, contains the synthetic cannabinoid 5F-ADB. 5F-ADB (5F-MDMB-PINACA) is a highly potent synthetic cannabinoid associated with 24 deaths in Europe. Unlike hashish, the substance is odorless.'
